554 shall constitute grounds for revocation or suspension of the
555 holder's certificate, unless the board determines the failure
556 to have been due to reasonable cause. In that case, the board
557 may impose a reinstatement fee not to exceed one hundred
558 dollars ($100), plus the total annual registration fees and
559 late renewal penalties whichthat the certified public
560 accountant or public accountant would have paid under this
Page 20

accountant or public accountant would have paid under this
HB59 Enrolled
561 chapter during the period when neither a permit nor inactive
